List all available endpoints

Source: R/avail_endpoints.R
avail_endpoints.Rd

List all available endpoints

avail_endpoints()

Value

A tibble::tibble with 2 columns. Endpoint contains the function for accessing the Delphi Epidata API endpoint along with a Description.

Examples

endps <- avail_endpoints()
print(endps, n = nrow(endps))
